      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n新しい仕事のオファーがあったと聞いたんですが",
      "startTime": 2.9421106335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "あぁ。地方でグラビア撮影の仕事だよ\n怜を指名で、モデルをお願いしたいらしい",
      "startTime": 10.2333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6078.187489499999,
          "startTime": 16.3115208228
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "先方から届いた資料をコピーしておいたから\n確認してみてくれ",
      "startTime": 16.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます。ふむふむ……あっ、この場所\n知ってます。ここってあの有名なひまわり畑ですよね！",
      "startTime": 24.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "以前、観光ガイドブックに掲載されているのを\n見たことがあります！",
      "startTime": 32.48596002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに有名な場所なのか？\nこの観光スポットは知らなかったよ",
      "startTime": 36.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "花好きの間では、よく話題に上がるらしいんです\nとはいえ、私もついこの間知ったんですけどね",
      "startTime": 44.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "実は最近、花を見ることにハマっているんです\n遙子さんと花屋巡りなんかもしてまして",
      "startTime": 53.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "昨日も遙子さんと一緒に\n花の名前と、花言葉を当てるゲームをしたんですよ",
      "startTime": 58.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_rei_14_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、そうですね……ネモフィラの花言葉が\nどういうものなのか、知ってますか？",
      "startTime": 68.9333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}